attributes.review:
hi loves!!😘 i downloaded this app hoping to be able to support our amazingggg president🍊🍊i was very disappointed when the app to FOREVER to download😫😫 but i knew it would be worth it😘🙌🏼 WRONG!! do not get this app!!!😡😡 unfortunately i learned the hard way😕🧚🏼‍♀️ i was greeted by the cheeto himself when i first opened the app and i realized i wasn’t wearing my trump 2020 merchandise!!!😡😭 i was so disgusted in myself i could almost feel his eyes looking me up and down in rage😖🤢🤢 i felt so ashamed i couldn’t look trump in the eyes.. so i went off the app so i would feel safe..WRONG AGAIN!!🤡🤡my house started shaking and my tummy didn’t feel good at all!😪😪i started having this feeling that his own son was in danger!! #freebarrontrump2020🥳🥳 after that there was a knock at my door.. i was so petrified to even open the door because i knew i would have to face my consequences for not showing my support😔😔but i overcame my fears and when i opened the door there was a package..🤗ahh phew i remember my amazon package was supposed to come!! i couldn’t wait to start using the new dog shampoo i got so i could smell like a dog🐕🐕🥰i love dogs😍😍WRONG!!! it wasn’t my amazon package!!😡🤬 but a bunch of chuck e. cheese animatronic heads!!!!😭👿 i was so scared but then a bunch of rats started to infest my house and i knew i couldn’t bare to live there anymore😔😔it was haunted👻👻i had to move.. and what’s even worse... MY DOG SHAMPOO NEVER CAME AND GOT LOST IN THE MAIL😭😭😭😭 moral of the story don’t get this app.. unless you want to lose everything you own🧚🏼‍♀️✨🧚🏼‍♀️

                           sincerely, a gen z member🥰🧚🏼‍♀️
attributes.title: lost a 🏡 and my dog shampoo😭
